Vous avez pose la question suivante sur DahiraAbrar le <%= @answer.question.created_at.to_s(:custom_datetime) %> <br />
<br />
<blockquote>
  <p><%= @answer.question.content %></p>
</blockquote>
<br /> <br />
Voici la reponse qui y a ete apporte:
<blockquote>
  <p><%= @answer.content %></p>
</blockquote>
<% if @answer.documents %>
<% @answer.documents.each_with_index do |doc, index| %>
<%= link_to "Reference #{index+1}", url_for(doc) %> <br />
<%end %>
<%end%>
<p>
  Dahira Abrar
</p>